title: Chance The Rapper Ranks All Of Kanye West's Albums
text:
A photo posted by Chance The Rapper (@chancetherapper) on Sep 1, 2014 at 11:22am PDT 
However, that wasn’t the end of it. West eventually asked Chance to be on his album, The Life of Pablo , in 2016. His bars on “Ultralight Beam” were named HipHopDX’s Verse of the Year . Since then, Chance’s position in the rap community has only continued to skyrocket and it wouldn’t be surprising if he teamed up with his idol again. For now, Chano continues to show his love for Yeezy, ranking all eight of West’s albums in the order he believes is accurate. Check out the full list above.
